These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: woodworking, rock-climbing, cooking, hiking, puzzles, video-games, skydiving
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, canadian, chinese, mexican, nigerian, thai
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the chinese##1
 2. the mexican is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 4. the canadian is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is in the middle##1
 6. the argentine is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the argentine##1
 8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the canadian is on the left of the australian##1
10. the chinese is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Hobby           | puzzles | hiking | rock-climbing | cooking | woodworking | video-games | skydiving |
| Nationality   | argentine    | mexican   | chinese      | nigerian | canadian    | australian    | thai         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: lily, rose, zinnia, poppy, marigold, daffodil, dahlia
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, funk, gospel, pop, punk, rock, soul
 1. the fan of punk is the person who growspoppy##1
 2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 3. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
 4. the person who growsrose is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 7. the fan of punk is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 9. the fan of soul is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
10. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Flower          | lily | rose | marigold | poppy | daffodil | dahlia | zinnia |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | gospel   | pop   | punk      | d&b       | soul       | rock     |

