.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: corn, cucumber, lemon, lettuce, onion, pepper, spinach
The people use 7 different means of transport: motorbike, car, roller, airplane, train, taxi, quad-bike
 1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 2. the person eating onion is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 3. the person driving the car is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 4. the person eating corn is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is the person eating onion##1
 6. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 8. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 9. the person eating pepper is the person driving the airplane##1
10. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
11. the person driving the airplane is in the middle##1
12. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | cucumber | onion     | lemon  | pepper       | corn       | spinach  | lettuce   |
| Transport    | taxi  | motorbike | quad-bike | airplane | car | roller | train |

