.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: dubstep, metal, indie, r&b, gospel, blues, punk
7 different pets are kept: dog, fish, frog, goldfish, guinea-pig, horse, snake
 1. the fan of metal is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the owner of the fish is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 3. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the fan of blues##1
 6. the fan of gospel is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 8. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 9. the fan of r&b is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Music-Genre   | metal | indie | blues     | r&b | punk | gospel | dubstep |
| Pet     | snake   | frog    | guinea-pig | horse     | dog         | goldfish     | fish        |

