.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, drama, martial-arts, satire, time-travel
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: volleyball, biathlon, snowboarding, skiing, water-polo, surfing, skateboarding
 1. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 4. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | time-travel | drama | martial-arts | satire     | animation | crime |
| Sport     | surfing | skiing      | skateboarding | snowboarding    | water-polo | biathlon   | volleyball  |

