 5. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the fan of dubstep##1
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
