.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-9::.
There 7 different types of food: broccoli, corn, grapes, kiwi, papaya, radish, watermelon
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, tea, 7up, almond-milk, iced-tea, lemonade, juice
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 4. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating radish##1
 7. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 8. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating corn##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
11. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |   3    |    4     |   5    |     6      |   7    |
| Food        | corn | broccoli | grapes | kiwi     | radish | watermelon | papaya |
| Beverage   | lemonade | almond-milk  | juice    | water | iced-tea | tea       | 7up   |

