 7. the person who's birthday is in march is the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
10. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's birthday is in april##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |      2      |      3      |    4    |     5     |    6    |   7   |
